<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 15:15:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>普京称俄罗斯应考虑限制铀、钛和镍的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/putin-says-russia-should-consider-restricting-exports-uranium-titanium-nickel-2024-09-11/</link><description>俄罗斯总统普京周三表示，莫斯科应考虑限制铀、钛和镍的出口，以报复西方。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 14:48:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/putin-says-russia-should-consider-restricting-exports-uranium-titanium-nickel-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称如果面临威胁可能与中国“联合”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-could-combine-with-china-if-they-faced-threat-2024-09-11/</link><description>俄罗斯周三表示，其与中国的伙伴关系并非针对第三国，但如果面临美国的威胁，两国可以“结合潜力”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 14:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-it-could-combine-with-china-if-they-faced-threat-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国队对阵智利队赢得戴维斯杯揭幕战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/united-states-win-davis-cup-opener-against-chile-2024-09-11/</link><description>美国队周三战胜了智利队，开始了戴维斯杯决赛小组赛阶段的比赛，尽管多名顶级单打选手缺席。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:52:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/united-states-win-davis-cup-opener-against-chile-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>印度将对从中国和越南进口的部分钢铁征收高达30%的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-impose-up-30-tariffs-some-steel-imports-china-vietnam-2024-09-11/</link><description>印度财政部的一项命令显示，印度将对从中国和越南进口的部分钢铁产品征收12%至30%的关税，以保护和促进当地工业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 12:36:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-impose-up-30-tariffs-some-steel-imports-china-vietnam-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>研究称，零排放卡车价格需要下降 50% 才能与柴油竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/emissions-free-truck-prices-need-drop-by-50-compete-with-diesel-study-says-2024-09-11/</link><description>咨询公司麦肯锡周三发布的一项研究称，无排放卡车的价格需要下降一半，才能成为柴油车型的负担得起的替代品，这是帮助实现欧盟气候目标的必要步骤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/emissions-free-truck-prices-need-drop-by-50-compete-with-diesel-study-says-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国将出台广泛措施改善保险业、防范风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issue-broad-measures-improve-insurance-sector-prevent-risks-2024-09-11/</link><description>一份声明称，中国国务院周三表示，将出台具体指导意见，加强保险业监管，防范保险业风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issue-broad-measures-improve-insurance-sector-prevent-risks-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国孙俊浩否认中国关于足球比赛造假的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-koreas-son-jun-ho-denies-chinese-accusations-soccer-match-fixing-2024-09-11/</link><description>周三，韩国足球运动员孙俊浩含泪否认了中国当局对他在中国踢球时参与假球和贿赂的指控，并表示他是在胁迫下做出的虚假供述。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:38:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/south-koreas-son-jun-ho-denies-chinese-accusations-soccer-match-fixing-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：通胀观察的迅速变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-11/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>独家：三星电子计划部分部门全球裁员高达30%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-elec-plans-global-job-cuts-up-30-some-divisions-sources-say-2024-09-11/</link><description>三位直接了解此事的消息人士告诉路透社，全球最大的智能手机、电视和存储芯片制造商三星电子正在削减部分部门高达 30% 的海外员工。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 09:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-elec-plans-global-job-cuts-up-30-some-divisions-sources-say-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙将无视下议院对委内瑞拉反对派的承认</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/spain-ignore-lower-houses-recognition-venezuelan-opposition-2024-09-11/</link><description>首相表示，西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯的政府不会考虑议会投票承认委内瑞拉反对派候选人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯为有争议的总统选举的获胜者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 09:37:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/spain-ignore-lower-houses-recognition-venezuelan-opposition-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国美的集团将在香港上市时将股票定价定为区间上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-midea-group-price-shares-top-range-hong-kong-listing-sources-say-2024-09-11/</link><description>四位直接了解情况的人士表示，中国家电制造商美的集团将在香港上市时将股价定在指示性区间的最高价，以筹集至少 34.6 亿美元的资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-midea-group-price-shares-top-range-hong-kong-listing-sources-say-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>教皇方济各登陆新加坡；宗教间对话、气候问题提上议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pope-francis-arrives-singapore-last-stop-12-day-tour-2024-09-11/</link><description>教皇方济各周三下午从东帝汶抵达新加坡，预计他将重点关注宗教间对话，并加强天主教会在这个天主教会占少数的地区的存在。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:29:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pope-francis-arrives-singapore-last-stop-12-day-tour-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>华为 Mate XT 激起中国人的自豪感，但 2,800 美元的售价遭到批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-tri-foldable-phone-stirs-chinese-pride-2800-price-tag-panned-2024-09-11/</link><description>华为新款三折叠智能手机在中国点燃了民族主义自豪感，社交媒体上热议华为的支持者认为，尽管受到美国制裁，华为仍然有能力在创新上超越苹果，尽管许多人对这款手机 2,800 美元的售价犹豫不决。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-tri-foldable-phone-stirs-chinese-pride-2800-price-tag-panned-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>外交部表示中方对美国操纵香港问题表示关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-concerned-about-us-manipulation-hong-kong-issues-says-foreign-ministry-2024-09-11/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周三表示，中方对美国操纵香港问题、打压香港发展表示关切。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 07:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-concerned-about-us-manipulation-hong-kong-issues-says-foreign-ministry-2024-09-11/</guid></item><item><title>农化公司先正达在瑞士裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/agrichemicals-company-syngenta-cuts-jobs-switzerland-2024-09-11/</link><description>农用化学品公司先正达 (Syngenta) 周三表示，由于今年农作物保护业务大幅下滑，该公司将在巴塞尔瑞士总部裁员 10% 以上。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 06:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/agrichemicals-company-syngenta-cuts-jobs-switzerland-2024-09-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>